---
title: Gourmet Venison & Beef Cheeseburger with Bacon Jam, Spiced Potato Fries & Truffle Mayo
description: You can never, ever go wrong with bacon in a burger. We've combined ours with caramelised onion chutney to create an out-of-this-world bacon jam! Add gooey Cheddar, a juicy beef-venison patty and peppery salad leaves, and you're in for a super gourmet burger to rival any pub version!

